Package: ggmapcn
Title: Customizable China and Global Map Visualizations
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Liang", "Ren", email = "rl23@mails.tsinghua.edu.cn", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2360-7900"))
Description: A 'ggplot2' extension centered on map visualization of China
    and the globe. Provides customizable projections, boundary styles,
    coordinate grids, scale bars, and buffer zones for thematic maps,
    suitable for spatial data analysis and cartographic visualization.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
